      "side": 1,
      "message": "This seems somewhat fragile. Don\u0027t we always add new color types to the end of the enum to avoid breaking old serializations? We already have an 8 bit format thats \u003e kRGBA_F1Norm, it just happens to not be supported as a SkSurface (kR8G8_unorm).",
